A man is suspected to have committed suicide in Embu. Nyaga Ndeke&rsquo;s lifeless body was found dangling from a macadamia tree in Kiathitu village, Embu North subcounty, on Saturday. Residents reported the matter to area assistant chief Joseph Muriuki.Muriuki said Ndeke was last seen in a nearby shopping on Friday. He said the reason for committing suicide was not immediately known, he did not leave behind a note.Muriuki said they found a bunch of miraa in his pocket.He urged residents to not keep quiet with their problems, but to share them with their friends to avoid such incidents.